      <title>默默的擦亮手里的武器，准备下一次战斗</title>
      <link>http://blog.geyuxu.com/posts/archives/20190223-others-%E9%BB%98%E9%BB%98%E7%9A%84%E6%93%A6%E4%BA%AE%E6%89%8B%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%88%98%E6%96%97/</link>
